contentList.content: Expert Assassin
You know the skills every good assassin has picked up. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_InfiltrationExpertise">Infiltration Expertise</LSTag>.
Master Thief
You've mastered all the skills a thief can learn. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_SupremeSneak">Supreme Sneak</LSTag>.
Rogue Imposter

The world may mistake you for a rogue but deep down, you know you aren't one. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Hide_BonusAction">Cunning Action: Hide</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Dash_CunningAction">Cunning Action: Dash</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Disengage_CunningAction">Cunning Action: Disengage</LSTag>.
Uncivilized
You think you're a barbarian, you are...but not the kind you want to be.
Serial Killer

You once saw a tiefling slaughtering her way through enemies, you tried to imitate her but failed. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_IntimidatingPresence">Intimidating Presence</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_FrenziedStrike">Frenzied Strike</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Throw_FrenziedThrow">Frenzied Throw</LSTag>.
Delusional
You pretend to be an animal when you're angry...and it works. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_SpeakWithAnimals_Barbarian">Speak With Animals</LSTag>.
Tone-deaf Bard

You can just barely convince someone you are a bard. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_SongOfRest">Song of Rest</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Countercharm">Countercharm</LSTag>.
Novice Cleric
You know some basic things about being a cleric. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_TurnUndead">Turn Undead</LSTag>.
Novice Fighter

You have picked up some basic knowledge related to combat. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_SecondWind">Second Wind</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_ActionSurge">Action Surge</LSTag>.
Veteran Fighter

You were seasoned through blood and battle, you walk through battlefields with an air of confidence. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_SecondWind">Second Wind</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_ActionSurge">Action Surge</LSTag>.
Godless Paladin

You call yourself a Paladin but you've never taken an oath. You emit an aura of <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_AuraOf_Protection">protection</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_AuraOf_Courage">courage</LSTag>...and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_AuraOf_Hate">hate</LSTag>.
Novice Ranger
You've picked up the basic skills of being a ranger.
Adept Stalker

You are proficient in the art of stalking prey. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Hide_DreadAmbusher">Dread Ambusher: Hide</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_UmbralCloak">Umbral Shroud</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_DisguiseSelf">Disguise Self</LSTag>.
Adept Hunter
You are proficient in hunting prey. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Volley">Volley</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Whirlwind">Whirlwind</LSTag>.
Apex Predator

Your prey always end up dead and few things can escape from you. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Volley">Volley</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Whirlwind">Whirlwind</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Hide_DreadAmbusher">Dread Ambusher: Hide</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_UmbralCloak">Umbral Shroud</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_DisguiseSelf">Disguise Self</LSTag>.
Competent Spellcaster
You can differentiate friend from foe unlike some other spellcasters.
Seer

Occasionally, you catch a glimpse of the future and predict your opponent's actions. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Darkvision_ThirdEye">Third Eye: Darvision</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_SeeInvisibility_ThirdEye">Third Eye: See Invisibility</LSTag>.
Elemental Lord
You may not hold absolute dominion over the elements but they bend before your will, the elements almost seem to hesitate before you. Gain resistance to Fire, Cold, Lightning and Thunder damage.
Insightful Spellcaster
You've learned to manipulate spells to a higher degree.
Outer Gods' Servant
You've made a pact with something powerful and unknown, possibly outside of reality itself.
Timeworn Paladin

You swore an oath long ago, all who can attest to it are gone and your god has long been silent. Only you know if your faith remains strong but those around you can perceive an <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_AuraOf_Devotion">aura of devotion</LSTag> and are <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_AuraOf_Warding">warded</LSTag> from spells.
Shapeshifter

You may be mistaken for a druid but a druid you most certaintly are not. Your repertoire includes the following <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape">wildshapes:</LSTag> <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Badger">badger</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Spider">spider</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Wolf_Dire">wolf</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Cat">cat</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_DeepRothe">rothe</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Wildshape_Panther">panther</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Owlbear">owlbear</LSTag>.
Impatient Monk

The life of a monk was not one you were cut out for but that doesn't mean you learnt nothing. You've embraced the shadows and gained total control of yourself during combat. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_ShadowStep">Shadow Step</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Hide_ShadowArts">Hide</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_PassWithoutTrace_Monk">Pass Without Trace</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Darkness_Monk">Darkness</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Darkvision_Monk">Darkvision</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Silence_Monk">Silence</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_CloakOfShadows_Monk">Cloak of Shadows</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_MinorIllusion">Minor Illusion</LSTag>.
Descendant of Dragons
The blood of a dragon runs through your veins. <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Projectile_Fly_DragonWings">Flying</LSTag> comes naturally.
Conjurer

You've dabbled in the arts of conjuration and call yourself a wizard. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_CreateWater_MinorConjuration">Minor Conjuration: Create Water</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_BenignTransposition_Teleport">Benign Transposition: Teleport</LSTag>.
Mind Master
Your mind is your most important asset, you've mastered it and made it a fortress. You have achieved <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_StillnessOfMind">Stillness of Mind</LSTag>.
Stormborn
There is a certain calm that washes over you during a storm, as if it's welcoming you home.
Tainted
Your bloodline is one that has been sullied by fey energies. You can radiate your <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_FeyPresence_Container">Fey Presence</LSTag> at will.
Eldritch Worshipper
You have made a pact with some unknown entity residing in the Far Realm.
Student of Undeath
You have always found the dead to be both better company and more interesting than the living.
Mortal Instrument
You have great power granted from your patron, their goals likely destructive...but such things are not your concern.
Shaolin Monk

You have mastered mind, body, soul and fist. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_OpenHandTechnique_Knock">topple</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_OpenHandTechnique_NoReactions">stagger</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_OpenHandTechnique_Push">push</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_KiResonation_Punch">Ki Resonation: Punch</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_KiResonation_Blast">Ki Resonation: Blast</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WholenessOfBody">Wholeness of Body</LSTag>.
Swordsinger
Your title had no relation to your skill with the sword, you meant it to be a bit more literal, a bard with a blade. Your repertoire includes all flourishes.
Wordweaver
You spin tales and weave words to your liking.
Witness of Heroes
You wander the land to witness and keep alive the deeds and memories of the mighty.
Lunar Druid

You are sworn to the moon and can draw on its power to transform yourself. Your repertoire includes the following <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat"> combat wildshapes:</LSTag> <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat_Badger">badger</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat_Spider">spider</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat_Wolf_Dire">wolf</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat_Cat">cat</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat_DeepRothe">rothe</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat_Bear_Polar">bear</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat_Raven">raven</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Wildshape_Combat_Panther">panther</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_WildShape_Combat_Owlbear">owlbear</LSTag>.
Fungal Druid

You manipulate spores to augment yourself and harm your foes. Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_HaloOfSpores">Halo of Spores</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_SymbioticEntity">Symbiotic Entity</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_ChillTouch">Chill Touch</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Blindness">Blindness</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_DetectThoughts">Detect Thoughts</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_AnimateDead">Animate Dead</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_GaseousForm">Gaseous Form</LSTag> and <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_FungalInfestation">Fungal Infestation</LSTag>.
Unstable Sorcerer
Your powers come from ancient forces of chaos, they churn within you, waiting to burst free at any time.
Transmigrator
Your soul is not native to this body or even this universe, inexplicably, none seem to be the wiser. Fortunately, you seem to have assimilated the skills and memories of your host.
Reincarnator
How many lives you have lived, how much you have experienced, only you know.
Regressor

A dream? A hallucination? Haven't you been through this before? You've gone backwards in time. At least you remember your past experiences..or are they future ones? Your repertoire includes <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_AuraOf_Courage">aura of courage</LSTag>.
Enigmatic Harbinger

Something beyond your comprehension has bestowed upon you the power to smite your foes. No oaths to be sworn, it only seeks amusement. You have been granted <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Smite_Divine">Divine Smite</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Smite_Wrathful">Wrathful Smite</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Smite_Searing">Searing Smite</LSTag>, <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Smite_Thunderous">Thunderous Smite</LSTag> and more.
Enigma
Something about you is different, it's difficult to pinpoint. Is it in your blood, your soul, your skills and capabilities? It's hard to place you in the common categories.

Pragmatic
You have always thought one should diversify their skillset if they have the means.
